<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verification OTP</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #2c7be5;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .otp-box {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #f0f4ff;
        color: #2c7be5;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999999;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 20px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">School Payment Portal</div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>
          Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your verification
          process in the <strong>School Payment & Dashboard System</strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="otp-box">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>
          This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Do not share this code with anyone for your security.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thanks,<br />
          <strong>School Payment Support Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} School Payment Portal. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
